==English==

===Noun===
'''reciprocation'''

# The act of [[reciprocate|reciprocating]]; [[interchange]] of acts; a [[mutual]] giving and returning; as, the reciprocation of kindness.
# [[alternate|Alternate]] [[recurrence]] or action; as, the reciprocation of the sea in the flow and ebb of tides.

